CustomName就是箱子或者实体的名字
例子
/summon zombie ~ ~ ~ {CustomName:"\"我是僵尸\""}
/setblock ~ ~ ~ chest{CustomName:"\"我是个箱子\""}
/setblock ~ ~ ~ minecraft:dispenser{CustomName:"\"我是投掷器\""}






